{"tid":2028712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家真係好叻","createTime":"2020-05-22T02:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T04:19:38.000Z","uid":13513,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"abd09cd678c5527aa6c098df8eddc196b4b45879","tid":2028712,"uid":13513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"大家諗下 我地用左一年時間就逼到中共要行呢一步 真攬炒<br />\n<br />\n雖然話咁啱佢自己都外憂內患重重 <br />\n<br />\n但無可否認我地係打響左頭炮 <br />\n<br />\n而且一打就打到班人面獸心既狗官 中共狗全部現曬形<br />\n<br />\n真係要俾啲掌聲自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 有得移民既就做好research<br />\n<br />\n無得or唔想走既大家 記住要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"> 買vpn </span></span><br />\n<br />\n繼續煲熟<span style=\"color: navy;\">藍</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">黃</span>鋪既分佈<br />\n<br />\n做好準備係TWITTER見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a778e4ded9496009173ad626e58cc7d9e57d99d","tid":2028712,"uid":269515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiJO5UK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiJO5UK.jpg&h=7797c282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【如果你覺得好無力，不妨諗下...難道習近平又過得好好？】<br />\n<br />\n「黎明前嘅黑暗係最黑暗」係句好詩意嘅說話。如果通俗少少講，就係：有打開機都知，隻boss開始暴走放大招嘅時候，其實就係佢殘血就死之時。<br />\n中共之所以呢個時候推國安法，唔係因為佢管治能力有幾高明或者幾有作為，而係相反，正正顯示到佢地已經冇招。一個喺管治上已經無招可用嘅政權，敗亡亦不過係時候問題。"},{"pid":"297441502d30778e55ff0e2b67c3e31c80551bc8","tid":2028712,"uid":13513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gkeR3Jj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgkeR3Jj.jpg&h=4ce487e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95e5e6cb11e652df18e38a6671a09f31e956ac6b","tid":2028712,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8953c8d967dd4a896dbb57ad29e4f6a1fa1177","tid":2028712,"uid":13513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"VPN VPN VPN"},{"pid":"5e5c8f8daf30582b303a301dc67f14903782a5d8","tid":2028712,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:01:51.000Z","msg":"多謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c274b391963f2dd74ac028d3880870f6b2e0c6bf","tid":2028712,"uid":13513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:01:59.000Z","msg":"TWITTER TWITTER TWITTER"},{"pid":"13b0a790ae8b53976e17c6e9041a8df13416e009","tid":2028712,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"仍需努力！"},{"pid":"dec49251cffdc6d7371070142d9deeb82c9fc590","tid":2028712,"uid":13513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5e5c8f8daf30582b303a301dc67f14903782a5d8","tid":2028712,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:01:51.000Z","msg":"多謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"勇武當然唔話得 但和理非都做左好多野 兩個都咁叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd6ee7de9cb75a300c9a044a9119744a790d194","tid":2028712,"uid":10503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"唔好俾佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243a8879cc6b963dd19be6cf4b3f37bef09b74af","tid":2028712,"uid":261082,"